fault at runtime on x64); aligned local scratch -> alias-safe (out may == left/right)
    - _DEBUG numeric-equivalence oracle vs scalar xf_matrix_3x4 (1e-4f) proving the lane-3-only 
translate
    - no #ifdef _M_X64 fork; 0 C4235; scratch x64 cl /c clean + 32-bit sharedMath ClCompile clean 
