commit e9edaeca8e59af301bf7a56379326b2bace7ca1f
Author: Kenny Long <kenny.alan.long@gmail.com>
Date:   Mon Jun 15 18:40:57 2026 -0500

    feat(31-02): port FloatingPointUnit x87 asm to CRT FP API with x87<->_MCW_* boundary translation
    
    - replace __asm fnstcw/fldcw with _controlfp_s; module stays in x87-hardware layout, translate 
only at get/set boundary (review #1a)
    - x87LayoutToMcw / mcwToX87Layout: faithful per-field ROUND/PRECISION/EXCEPTION translation, 
exception-mask polarity preserved (set=masked)
    - P_24 precision RETAINED on 32-bit (named decision, VERIFY-01 door-snap watch-item); omitted on 
x64 via #if defined(_M_X64) (no _MCW_PC to CRT -> avoids invalid-param handler); never __control87_2
    - _DEBUG round-trip self-check (getControlWord->setControlWord->getControlWord) proves 
translation lossless
    - 0 C4235; scratch x64 cl /c clean
---
 .../src/win32/FloatingPointUnit.cpp                | 167 ++++++++++++++++++++-
 1 file changed, 161 insertions(+), 6 deletions(-)

