commit 8479fb6babd737774c4af69e04ddb9a9e682a888
Author: Kenny Long <kenny.alan.long@gmail.com>
Date:   Mon Jun 15 20:35:20 2026 -0500

    fix(31-07): port trivial B-GAP-1 __asm survivors to intrinsics/normal fns
    
    - ByteOrder.cpp: 4 naked bswap ntohl/htonl/ntohs/htons -> _byteswap_ulong/_byteswap_ushort
    - RegexServices.cpp + Direct3d9/Direct3d11 MemoryManagerHook.cpp + RenderWorldServices.cpp:
      naked allocate-hook trampolines -> normal fns forwarding to MemoryManager::allocate,
      leak owner captured via _ReturnAddress() (preserves the [ebp+4] caller-addr owner)
    - all 5 TUs (6 files) compile x64-clean in the scratch harness (exit 0, 0 C4235)
    - no #ifdef _M_X64 fork; intrinsics compile both bitnesses (D-05)

